## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The data is primarily from Western contexts, which may not fully represent global trends. Additionally, the complexity of human behavior means that no single theory can entirely explain the gender gap in crime rates. Further research, particularly in diverse cultural settings, is necessary to gain a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.

